text.tspan: Annual change in male population aged 90 to 99 years, 1951 to 2100
Population yearly increment, estimated as the difference between the population on 1st of July of the year
indicated and the population a year before. This only includes males aged 90-99. Projections from 2024
onwards are based on the UN's low scenario.
Data source: UN, World Population Prospects (2024)
